{"data":[{"id":564183329,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":307595822,"title":"高中生对哥德巴赫猜想的证明有哪些错误？","question_type":"normal","created":1546272354,"updated_time":1546301579,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/307595822","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"eddfe964f26088401b93c13f52e1a1fd","url_token":"wang-peng-81-22","name":"凡人","avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/b28bf1f238f07b5b1751a2a821284238_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/b28bf1f238f07b5b1751a2a821284238_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/eddfe964f26088401b93c13f52e1a1fd","user_type":"people","headline":"我是个杂家","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":207,"is_followed":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/564183329","thumbnail":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-83987f5a6b84570993375812fb4df005_200x112.jpg","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546339290,"updated_time":1546340049,"extras":"","is_copyable":false,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":15,"comment_count":9,"is_sticky":false,"admin_closed_comment":false,"comment_permission":"all","can_comment":{"reason":"","status":true},"reshipment_settings":"need_payment","content":"\u003cp\u003e首先，大家的纠错和嘲讽，都是这高中少年该受的，自己做的选择，自己要承担后果。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e但是，这孩子，没违法犯罪吧？没侵犯其他人利益吧？而某些人，用极其狭隘的心胸，对该少年的行为上纲上线的进行批斗，什么对学术的侮辱都来了，恨不能把这孩子踩到泥土里永世不得翻身，恨不得让这孩子给所有网友磕头谢罪，甚至觉得网络暴力有理了，甚至觉得这孩子因为网络暴力自闭、抑郁、甚至自杀都是活该，我觉得有点过分了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e贴两个典型吧。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-454e08b2bdb95dcb62febb4fb31ac30d_b.jpg\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"660\" data-rawheight=\"127\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-024d0950d348c10646adcbea941be4ad_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"660\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-454e08b2bdb95dcb62febb4fb31ac30d_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='660'%20height='127'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"660\" data-rawheight=\"127\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-024d0950d348c10646adcbea941be4ad_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"660\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-454e08b2bdb95dcb62febb4fb31ac30d_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-454e08b2bdb95dcb62febb4fb31ac30d_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-d327998f5a84455a4606140362f55016_b.jpg\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"648\" data-rawheight=\"210\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-bb9985a52c3d3aea5933b0346f356441_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"648\" data-original=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-d327998f5a84455a4606140362f55016_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='648'%20height='210'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"648\" data-rawheight=\"210\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-bb9985a52c3d3aea5933b0346f356441_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"648\" data-original=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-d327998f5a84455a4606140362f55016_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-d327998f5a84455a4606140362f55016_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e一个高中的孩子装了波逼。。。。。直接就上升到科学工作者的形象问题和科学工作亵渎问题了。。。。我真的是。。。。科学工作的门槛什么时候这么低了？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e不拿诺奖不改名，这个id倒是充分体现了此人无比的清高与自傲，此人此时的心态，恐怕是觉得自己所从事的事业是无比的清高与伟大的，一个高中小屁孩，思考这些问题就是对自己的侮辱。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e说来也巧，今天刚好看了黑子的篮球last game，此人的想法倒是与纳什.戈尔多.jr的想法非常的相似呢：\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e你们这些日本猴子也配打篮球？你们打篮球就是对我的侮辱。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e你一个高中生也配思考哥猜？你提这两个字就是对我的侮辱。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e真心可怕。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e再贴另外一个声援不拿诺奖不改名的人士\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-eb55f6a4aff918ff706a224afcc2aec1_b.jpg\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"643\" data-rawheight=\"152\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-90542bcdee948b705b6b35e71027b94c_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"643\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-eb55f6a4aff918ff706a224afcc2aec1_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='643'%20height='152'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"643\" data-rawheight=\"152\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-90542bcdee948b705b6b35e71027b94c_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"643\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-eb55f6a4aff918ff706a224afcc2aec1_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-eb55f6a4aff918ff706a224afcc2aec1_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-bd2f66a0a1239144f059729ffc3008fc_b.jpg\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"653\" data-rawheight=\"167\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-c3ad669ac7aeb2c401d4b88cb62f19ad_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"653\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-bd2f66a0a1239144f059729ffc3008fc_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='653'%20height='167'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"653\" data-rawheight=\"167\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-c3ad669ac7aeb2c401d4b88cb62f19ad_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"653\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-bd2f66a0a1239144f059729ffc3008fc_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-bd2f66a0a1239144f059729ffc3008fc_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e不仅认为这孩子侮辱了数学工作者，而且把知乎的乱象归结于这个孩子身上，甚至认为这孩子错在把证明发到网上了，我觉得此人侮辱了“言论自由”四个字，侮辱了“我不同意你说的每一个字，但我愿誓死捍卫你说话的权利”这句话。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e当然，这个高中生可能是营销号，那是另外一个问题了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e这两个人，都把我拉黑了，辩论不过就拉黑，将心胸的狭隘体现的淋漓尽致。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e拉黑真是个好工具，可以直接向对方表示：“不听不听王八念经，反正我是对的你是错的你不用说了”。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e可惜我也不是什么心胸宽广的人呢，你们喜欢拉黑，我就给你们晒晒太阳。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e不过是一个有点过分中二的无知少年而已，不过就是装了个逼装大了然后装破了而已，年轻气盛，谁没装过逼呢？谁没自命不凡过呢？谁上学的时候没有过质疑权威的想法呢？如果无知都算侮辱的话，那全世界至少40亿人无时不刻的都在侮辱学术，甚至于嘲讽这个孩子的人中，有相当一部分也是学术水平不足的（比如揪着“负质数”本身不放的），那是不是同样也是在装逼呢，同样也是侮辱了学术呢？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e大家纠错也纠错了，嘲讽也嘲讽了，这孩子也认识到了自己的无知和浅薄，删文退场了，也算是个知错能改的少年，跟那些死犟不服的民科还是有本质区别的，他自己恐怕也认识到了几千网友的口水是多么恐怖，以后也不会轻易在公众平台发表看法了，人非圣贤孰能无过，得饶人处且饶人，别为了自己的口舌之快毁了一个孩子的一生。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","editable_content":"","excerpt":"首先，大家的纠错和嘲讽，都是这高中少年该受的，自己做的选择，自己要承担后果。但是，这孩子，没违法犯罪吧？没侵犯其他人利益吧？而某些人，用极其狭隘的心胸，对该少年的行为上纲上线的进行批斗，什么对学术的侮辱都来了，恨不能把这孩子踩到泥土里永世…","collapsed_by":"nobody","collapse_reason":"","annotation_action":[],"mark_infos":[],"relevant_info":{"is_relevant":false,"relevant_type":"","relevant_text":""},"suggest_edit":{"reason":"","status":false,"tip":"","title":"","unnormal_details":{"status":"","description":"","reason":"","reason_id":0,"note":""},"url":""},"is_labeled":false,"reward_info":{"can_open_reward":false,"is_rewardable":false,"reward_member_count":0,"reward_total_money":0,"tagline":""},"relationship":{"is_author":false,"is_authorized":false,"is_nothelp":false,"is_thanked":false,"voting":0,"upvoted_followees":[]}}],"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/307595822/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannota